      * L186: 	DISPLAY SPACE.
      * L187: 	DISPLAY "COMMAND> " WITH NO ADVANCING.
      * L188: 	ACCEPT COMMAND-WORD.
      * L189: 	IF COMMAND-LETTER = SPACE GO TO GET-COMMAND.
      * L190: 	IF COMMAND-C GO TO CLOSE-RMS-FILE.
      * L191: 	IF COMMAND-D GO TO DELETE-RMS-RECORD.
      * L192: 	IF COMMAND-R GO TO READ-RMS-RECORD.
